==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Restrict
<hw>Re*strict"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>restrictus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>restringere</ets>. See
<er>Restrain</er>.]</ety> <def>Restricted.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Restrict</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Restrict
<hw>Re*strict"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Restricted</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Restricting</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To restrain within bounds; to
limit; to confine; <as>as, to <ex>restrict</ex> worlds to a particular
meaning; to <ex>restrict</ex> a patient to a certain
diet.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- To limit; bound; circumscribe; restrain; repress;
curb; coerce.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Restriction</ent>⟦br⟧
